1
00:00:53,540 --> 00:00:57,060
=Starlit Bloom=

2
00:00:57,060 --> 00:01:00,060
=Episode 19=

3
00:01:25,080 --> 00:01:26,670
Since I've sent you back,

4
00:01:26,880 --> 00:01:27,910
I'll get going.

5
00:01:29,550 --> 00:01:30,360
Sure.

6
00:01:33,830 --> 00:01:34,640
Gu Liusu.

7
00:01:41,533 --> 00:01:42,720
Can you stay for a while?

8
00:01:49,270 --> 00:01:50,310
Today

9
00:01:50,390 --> 00:01:53,110
is the 103rd day

10
00:01:53,550 --> 00:01:55,190
since we met again.

11
00:01:57,100 --> 00:01:59,580
♪When everything before eyes♪

12
00:02:00,780 --> 00:02:03,180
♪In the flow of time♪

13
00:02:03,720 --> 00:02:05,240
But I never thought

14
00:02:08,110 --> 00:02:10,200
things would turn out this way.

15
00:02:14,270 --> 00:02:15,200
I'm really upset.

16
00:02:20,550 --> 00:02:22,200
For whatever I've done...

17
00:02:24,870 --> 00:02:25,870
I know

18
00:02:26,590 --> 00:02:28,990
you must think I was childish

19
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:30,550
and acting like a kid.

20
00:02:33,390 --> 00:02:34,710
But I just wanted

21
00:02:35,320 --> 00:02:36,870
people to know

22
00:02:39,040 --> 00:02:40,960
that I'm the one behind you.

23
00:02:41,500 --> 00:02:47,060
♪I'm feeling you from up on the hill♪

24
00:02:47,080 --> 00:02:47,870
Forgive me.

25
00:02:50,320 --> 00:02:51,990
I really didn't think that much.

26
00:02:58,360 --> 00:02:59,670
I just wondered

27
00:03:00,990 --> 00:03:02,920
if you'd be a little happier today.

28
00:03:08,830 --> 00:03:10,080
I just wondered

29
00:03:11,710 --> 00:03:13,760
what Liusu is doing today.

30
00:03:14,760 --> 00:03:16,080
Does she want coffee?

31
00:03:18,200 --> 00:03:19,710
Did someone buy her one?

32
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:28,430
If possible,

33
00:03:31,760 --> 00:03:33,960
I'd want to stay by your side

34
00:03:34,670 --> 00:03:36,200
like a kid.

35
00:03:36,990 --> 00:03:38,080
All right?

36
00:03:39,820 --> 00:03:47,420
♪All the melodies within me
exist in you as well♪

37
00:03:48,084 --> 00:03:49,150
I want to be pampered too.

38
00:03:49,333 --> 00:03:50,670
But who's there to pamper me?

39
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:53,670
Everyone wants a safe haven.

40
00:03:53,920 --> 00:03:55,520
But who's born to be one?

41
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:01,040
Don't go.

42
00:04:06,040 --> 00:04:09,040
♪Frozen memories♪

43
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:12,480
♪Faded moments gone by♪

44
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:15,640
♪Brought up by chance♪

45
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:19,640
♪Your name struck a chord in my heart♪

46
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:22,060
♪Funny, isn't it?♪

47
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:26,530
♪Only after losing you
did I see your love was worth keeping♪

48
00:04:27,220 --> 00:04:29,820
♪I hate myself for not being brave,
for not trying♪

49
00:04:29,900 --> 00:04:34,200
♪For letting you slip away
into the crowd with my own hands♪

50
00:04:34,440 --> 00:04:35,780
♪Look at us♪

51
00:04:35,980 --> 00:04:38,460
♪Like two planets
that were never meant to meet♪

52
00:04:38,540 --> 00:04:40,860
♪Colliding across the sky♪

53
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:43,620
Stop!

54
00:04:45,220 --> 00:04:48,020
♪Does that still count as luck?♪

55
00:04:48,300 --> 00:04:49,830
♪Look at us♪

56
00:04:49,830 --> 00:04:50,680
Sorry.

57
00:04:50,711 --> 00:04:51,955
I can't keep losing control.

58
00:04:52,520 --> 00:04:54,030
Stop before it's too late.

59
00:04:55,640 --> 00:05:00,360
♪Maybe we were never meant to be♪

60
00:05:17,560 --> 00:05:18,640
(You know this.)

61
00:05:19,888 --> 00:05:21,577
(You two aren't right for each other.)

62
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:25,880
(Perhaps)

63
00:05:27,311 --> 00:05:28,960
(this is for the best for both of you.)

64
00:05:42,390 --> 00:05:43,590
You're back.

65
00:05:43,880 --> 00:05:44,830
Come on and sit.

66
00:05:48,470 --> 00:05:49,830
You bought a cake!

67
00:05:49,830 --> 00:05:50,680
Give it to me.

68
00:05:52,320 --> 00:05:54,150
So beautiful.

69
00:05:54,320 --> 00:05:55,120
Look.

70
00:05:55,960 --> 00:05:57,350
Happy birthday.

71
00:05:58,830 --> 00:06:00,560
See? I told you.

72
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:01,440
He cares about you.

73
00:06:01,440 --> 00:06:02,470
You didn't believe me.

74
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:06,120
It's your birthday today.

75
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:07,880
Why the long face?

76
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:09,520
Smile.

77
00:06:10,590 --> 00:06:11,680
Alright.

78
00:06:13,080 --> 00:06:14,150
Since you're back,

79
00:06:14,390 --> 00:06:16,200
come sit and eat.

80
00:06:18,200 --> 00:06:19,000
Okay.

81
00:06:19,790 --> 00:06:20,680
Do you want this?

82
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:21,680
Let me put it on for you.

83
00:06:21,710 --> 00:06:23,320
Let's eat first.

84
00:06:25,030 --> 00:06:26,440
We've got a lot of dishes today.

85
00:06:26,680 --> 00:06:28,200
I figured you might come back,

86
00:06:28,200 --> 00:06:29,640
so I made a few.

87
00:06:29,790 --> 00:06:31,560
They're all your favorites.

88
00:06:31,790 --> 00:06:32,640
Try them.

89
00:06:32,880 --> 00:06:35,200
I haven't seen you in a while.
You look tired.

90
00:06:44,080 --> 00:06:45,150
How does it taste?

91
00:06:47,080 --> 00:06:48,350
Nice.

92
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:53,640
Lu said these were your favorites
when you were a kid.

93
00:06:53,666 --> 00:06:55,622
I'm lucky to get to try them
because of you.

94
00:06:56,390 --> 00:06:57,830
Your dad cooked them himself.

95
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:59,440
Eat up.

96
00:07:01,200 --> 00:07:01,760
Okay.

97
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:12,168
(Tang Baozhu)
(Xingchen came back)

98
00:07:12,192 --> 00:07:13,710
(for his dad's birthday.)

99
00:07:15,440 --> 00:07:16,910
That night at the auction...

100
00:07:23,710 --> 00:07:24,640
Lin Xiang

101
00:07:24,640 --> 00:07:26,120
is a scoundrel.

102
00:07:29,910 --> 00:07:32,230
(Gu Liusu)
(There's nothing between us anymore.)

103
00:07:35,350 --> 00:07:38,790
I heard Mo Li covered that money
in the end.

104
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:40,350
I'm sorry.

105
00:07:42,030 --> 00:07:43,120
I was impulsive.

106
00:07:48,760 --> 00:07:51,030
If you can't even protect
the one you love,

107
00:07:51,200 --> 00:07:52,910
what's the point of being great?

108
00:07:53,960 --> 00:07:55,000
No need to apologize.

109
00:07:55,710 --> 00:07:57,520
I was just standing up

110
00:07:57,520 --> 00:07:59,000
for my future daughter-in-law.

111
00:08:01,760 --> 00:08:03,880
If you can't make
the person you care about happy,

112
00:08:04,270 --> 00:08:05,790
no success

113
00:08:05,790 --> 00:08:07,030
will make you happy.

114
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:15,000
It's your birthday today.

115
00:08:15,200 --> 00:08:16,590
We should all cheer up.

116
00:08:16,880 --> 00:08:17,520
Xingchen,

117
00:08:17,960 --> 00:08:20,880
let's sing for him.

118
00:08:21,200 --> 00:08:23,320
♪Happy birthday to you♪

119
00:08:23,470 --> 00:08:25,880
♪Happy birthday to you♪

120
00:08:26,120 --> 00:08:28,390
♪Happy birthday to you♪

121
00:08:28,640 --> 00:08:31,080
♪Happy birthday to you♪

122
00:08:32,710 --> 00:08:33,790
Thank you, Dear.

123
00:08:34,280 --> 00:08:34,920
Come on.

124
00:08:34,920 --> 00:08:37,960
Let's take a family photo.

125
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:38,750
Alright.

126
00:08:39,400 --> 00:08:40,200
Look here.

127
00:08:41,710 --> 00:08:42,750
Look here.

128
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:44,560
Smile.

129
00:08:50,822 --> 00:08:52,230
I'll send it to you once I edit it.

130
00:08:52,230 --> 00:08:52,630
Sure.

131
00:08:52,630 --> 00:08:53,688
I'll let you guys talk.

132
00:09:05,470 --> 00:09:06,280
Thank you, Dad.

133
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:18,080
Have you been keeping up lately?

134
00:09:19,710 --> 00:09:20,510
Yes.

135
00:09:21,088 --> 00:09:22,160
It's been going smoothly.

136
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:28,230
Mo Li is helping me.

137
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:31,710
He's been with the company
since his internship.

138
00:09:32,230 --> 00:09:33,830
He knows the business well.

139
00:09:34,870 --> 00:09:36,960
I'm glad he's guiding you.

140
00:09:37,830 --> 00:09:39,510
Since you've decided to come back,

141
00:09:39,870 --> 00:09:41,320
learn properly.

142
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:45,710
How's the food?

143
00:09:49,560 --> 00:09:50,510
Good.

144
00:09:52,280 --> 00:09:53,680
They taste like childhood.

145
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:58,510
If you like them,

146
00:09:58,920 --> 00:10:00,350
come home more often.

147
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:10,200
Xingchen,

148
00:10:11,560 --> 00:10:12,630
actually I

149
00:10:14,350 --> 00:10:15,630
owe you an apology.

150
00:10:19,560 --> 00:10:20,960
Back then,

151
00:10:22,350 --> 00:10:24,040
I really loved your mom.

152
00:10:24,750 --> 00:10:26,040
After she left,

153
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:28,200
I was a mess.

154
00:10:29,470 --> 00:10:30,870
All I could do was work.

155
00:10:32,680 --> 00:10:34,870
I tried to build a stable life

156
00:10:35,590 --> 00:10:37,200
to pave the way for you

157
00:10:38,590 --> 00:10:40,710
and give you a smooth future.

158
00:10:41,830 --> 00:10:42,870
But

159
00:10:44,920 --> 00:10:46,800
I never asked

160
00:10:46,800 --> 00:10:49,160
what you really wanted.

161
00:10:53,160 --> 00:10:54,560
It's my fault.

162
00:10:55,510 --> 00:10:56,750
I should apologize.

163
00:11:00,350 --> 00:11:01,680
I'm sorry.

164
00:11:20,630 --> 00:11:22,750
Can you forgive me?

165
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:37,590
Happy birthday.

166
00:11:44,350 --> 00:11:45,630
Dad.

167
00:12:08,040 --> 00:12:12,560
♪Happy birthday to you♪

168
00:12:14,960 --> 00:12:19,800
♪Happy birthday to you♪

169
00:12:21,040 --> 00:12:21,830
(Mr. Lu,)

170
00:12:21,844 --> 00:12:23,177
(we've tested and confirmed)

171
00:12:23,470 --> 00:12:25,160
(your DNA doesn't match.)

172
00:12:25,350 --> 00:12:27,750
So you're not his biological father.

173
00:12:28,960 --> 00:12:31,470
The boy's mother has a history
of hereditary mental illness.

174
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:34,920
This boy filed a report,
insisting you were his father.

175
00:12:35,230 --> 00:12:36,560
(That's why we contacted you.)

176
00:12:43,630 --> 00:12:44,560
Mom.

177
00:12:45,440 --> 00:12:47,230
The doctor said you can't go out.

178
00:12:50,160 --> 00:12:51,400
Your dad is Lu Jianhua.

179
00:12:51,400 --> 00:12:52,510
I'll take you to see him,

180
00:12:52,630 --> 00:12:53,560
okay?

181
00:12:53,560 --> 00:12:54,680
I'll take you to see him.

182
00:12:54,680 --> 00:12:56,111
I'll take you to see him, okay?

183
00:12:57,040 --> 00:12:57,920
Okay?

184
00:12:58,680 --> 00:13:00,470
Okay?

185
00:13:00,750 --> 00:13:02,710
Mom, don't scare me.

186
00:13:03,160 --> 00:13:04,200
Lu Jianhua.

187
00:13:05,400 --> 00:13:06,440
Lu Jianhua!

188
00:13:08,080 --> 00:13:09,800
Mom!

189
00:13:25,896 --> 00:13:31,216
=Starlit Bloom=

190
00:13:57,040 --> 00:14:01,600
♪But I can't escape♪

191
00:14:01,800 --> 00:14:04,400
♪The memories of you♪

192
00:14:05,960 --> 00:14:08,720
♪The harder I try to forget♪

193
00:14:08,920 --> 00:14:11,280
♪The more you come back to me♪

194
00:14:11,440 --> 00:14:18,560
♪Two hearts once in love
collide and shatter into pieces♪

195
00:14:18,840 --> 00:14:24,400
♪How can I piece myself together again?♪

196
00:14:24,920 --> 00:14:27,000
♪Funny, isn't it?♪

197
00:14:27,040 --> 00:14:32,040
♪Only after losing you
did I see your love was worth keeping♪

198
00:14:32,200 --> 00:14:34,760
♪I hate myself for not being brave,
for not trying♪

199
00:14:34,880 --> 00:14:39,080
♪For letting you slip away
into the crowd with my own hands♪

200
00:14:39,600 --> 00:14:45,960
♪Guess we just met at the wrong time♪

201
00:14:46,640 --> 00:14:52,600
♪What's left of our love
is nothing but ashes♪

202
00:14:53,240 --> 00:14:54,880
♪Look at us♪

203
00:14:54,920 --> 00:14:57,520
♪Like two planets
that were never meant to meet♪

204
00:14:57,600 --> 00:14:59,920
♪Colliding across the sky♪

205
00:14:59,960 --> 00:15:04,200
♪At the wrong time,
I found the one I loved most♪

206
00:15:04,240 --> 00:15:07,040
♪Does that still count as luck?♪

207
00:15:07,320 --> 00:15:08,680
♪Look at us♪

208
